1 operator of the farming operation.
2 (C) The farming operation did not operate a temporary labor
3 camp.
4 (b) Family farm does not include either of the following:
5 (i) A farming operation that is organized as a nonfamily
6 corporation or cooperation.
7 (ii) A farming operation with a hired manager who is not a
8 family member of the owner or operator of the farming operation.
9 (c) "Family member" means a spouse, child, stepchild, foster
10 child, parent, stepparent, or foster parent.
